[TITLE]
Pump with head + efficiency curves, speed pattern, and full energy pricing

[JUNCTIONS]
J1    50    120

[RESERVOIRS]
R1    10

[PUMPS]
;Head curve + relative speed + speed pattern
PU1    R1    J1    HEAD    HC1    SPEED    0.9    PATTERN    SPAT

[PIPES]
P1    J1    R1    1500    10    100    0    Open

[PATTERNS]
;Pump speed schedule
SPAT    1.0    0.8    0.6    0.8
;Per-pump energy price schedule
EPAT    1.0    1.5    2.0    1.5
;Global energy price schedule
GPAT    1.0    1.2    1.4    1.2

[CURVES]
;PUMP: three-point head curve (power-function form)
HC1    0      200
HC1    600    150
HC1    1200   60
;EFFICIENCY: flow vs efficiency %
EC1    200    55
EC1    600    78
EC1    1000   65

[ENERGY]
Global Efficiency    80
Global Price         0.09
Global Pattern       GPAT
Demand Charge        12.5
Pump    PU1    Efficiency    EC1
Pump    PU1    Price         0.11
Pump    PU1    Pattern       EPAT

[TIMES]
Duration              24:00
Hydraulic Timestep     1:00
Pattern Timestep       6:00
Report Timestep        1:00

[OPTIONS]
Units       GPM
Headloss    H-W

[END]
